<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="157" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="157">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="157">
Body oval. Elytron orange. Head pale yellow in males, black in females. Males with pronotum black except lateral and anterior margins pale yellow to yellowish white (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 5–8" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 5 - 8. Brachiacantha sp. 5 Brachiacantha bipartita, female 6 Brachiacantha aperta, female 7 Brachiacantha isthmena sp. nov. 8 Brachiacantha cachensis." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures5-8" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520867" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">5</figureCitation>
). Male genitalia with penis guide shorter than parameres, symmetrical, sides convergent at apical ⅓ (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 33–36" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figures 33 - 36. Brachiacantha bipartita, male genitalia 33 Tegmen, lateral view 34 Tegmen 35 Penis 36 Penis apex." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures33-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520873" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">34</figureCitation>
); parameres curved, wide at base, narrowed to apex, apex acute, setae arising from the apex and the convex side margin (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 33–36" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figures 33 - 36. Brachiacantha bipartita, male genitalia 33 Tegmen, lateral view 34 Tegmen 35 Penis 36 Penis apex." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures33-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520873" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">33</figureCitation>
); penis curved in basal 
<normalizedToken originalValue="½">1/2</normalizedToken>
, apex with long slender alae (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 33–36" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figures 33 - 36. Brachiacantha bipartita, male genitalia 33 Tegmen, lateral view 34 Tegmen 35 Penis 36 Penis apex." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures33-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520873" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">36</figureCitation>
), basal capsule crested, apex long and slender (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 33–36" captionStartId="F8" captionText="Figures 33 - 36. Brachiacantha bipartita, male genitalia 33 Tegmen, lateral view 34 Tegmen 35 Penis 36 Penis apex." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.56927.figures33-36" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520873" pageId="0" pageNumber="157">35</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
